<section id="quote">
    <h2>Famous Quote</h2>
    <blockquote>
        "But, soft! what light through yonder window breaks? It is the east and Juliet is the sun- Romeo (Act 1 Scene 5)."
        "O Romeo, Romeo! wherefore art thou Romeo? Deny thy father and refuse thy name; Or, if thou wilt not, be but sworn my love, And I'll no longer be a Capulet- Juliet (Act 2 Scene 2)."
        "i dreamt a dream tonight- Romeo (Act 1 Scene 4)"
        "A plague o' both your houses!-Mercutio ( Act 3 Scene 1)"
    </blockquote>
